headline: Better Artificial Intelligence Stock: Applied Materials vs. ASML
summary: Artificial intelligence (AI) is a growing industry worth your investment dollars.  Two such companies are Applied Materials (NASDAQ: AMAT) and ASML (NASDAQ: ASML).  Both supply machines to manufacture the microchips that make AI possible and are two of the world's biggest providers of this semiconductor equipment.
